<p>I hope you’ll join me at LLGT. I hope that you will not only enjoy what I have to say but that you will want to add to it your own voice. Really, without you, it’s just LLG.</p>



<p>I do have a couple of rules.</p>



<p>Rule #1: be kind. Kindness will go a long way.</p>



<p>Rule #2: keep it clean. This is a family oriented website. No comments with links to porn or casinos or anything that is not suited for little children.</p>



<p>That’s it. Just remember to laugh, learn and keep growing. And make sure you find someone to share your story with.</p>
